headline: Retail earnings: What to expect from 3 key categories
summary: Several retailers are set to report earnings this week, including Home Depot (HD), Target (TGT), TJX (TJX), Lowe's (LOW), Walmart (WMT), Ross (ROST), and Alibaba (BABA). Yahoo Finance Senior Reporter Brooke DiPalma outlines what investors are watching for from the retail earnings prints.
